{"tid":1353914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7月27日】不要被情緒主導，我地行使嘅，係有理性嘅武力！","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T22:07:36.000Z","uid":273854,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e33dd6e38983fbb754679771cea5e4ffd650150","tid":1353914,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"不要復仇，不要暴力<br />\n復仇同暴力都係單純發洩自己情緒<br />\n正如我地屌黑警，屌牛屎佬<br />\n係屌佢地濫用暴力，發洩自己情緒<br />\n而唔係使用合理武力, 點到即止<br />\n(以武止武)<br />\n<br />\n我地不是打不還手<br />\n我地不是和理非<br />\n但我地同嗰班禽獸嘅分別<br />\n係我地係<span style=\"color: red;\">有理性咁去使用武力</span><br />\n<br />\n記住我地嘅目的: <span style=\"color: red;\">挑戰政府嘅管治威信</span><br />\n記住我地短暫嘅訴求: <span style=\"color: red;\">反警黑合作，追究捉拿白衫暴徒</span><br />\n記住我地最終嘅訴求: <span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"ea654d646c35c489294aabed71dbb327f52bb8d5","tid":1353914,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"e2d602d5beaaa4a441f690bd488422e9614a56a5","tid":1353914,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"228d8b64339ed9d4da44a29edfd85abad6639b52","tid":1353914,"uid":41611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e33433a86b8ed3ce71a281a3d23508561c52e8","tid":1353914,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv6cWf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv6cWf.jpg&h=69de2f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好殺人放火姦淫擄掠就得，入元朗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0041316e561427d7fd6f1d3062e32e84a13e2d3d","tid":1353914,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"100c913b68795844a5f